{"tid":2056160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江西一縣再拆26處教堂十字架  耶教：我唔知 我睇唔到","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:00.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9270a85e7fad6ce726008ceae3db18ba5b7dba","tid":2056160,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"隨著中共官方宣布武漢疫情解封，中國各地政府繼續強化打壓宗教場所，江西省是基督教受打壓迫害的重災區之一。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》多次報道，今年4月份，江西省大量基督教三自教堂遭受地方政府打壓。據新收到的消息顯示，防疫隔離措施緩解後兩個月內，九江市都昌縣至少有26處三自教堂十字架遭政府強拆，教堂內被強制安裝監控設備。<br />\n<br />\n4月8日，該省各級政府官員到都昌縣大樹鄉福音堂進行檢查。5天後，縣政府人員以「十字架太高不安全」為由要求福音堂負責人拆除十字架，並威脅「若不服從就拆教堂」。政府人員還要求在教堂內安裝監控攝像頭，為此教堂負責人花費了1000元人民幣（下同。約140美金）。<br />\n「政府告訴我們說安裝攝像頭是為了防止『邪教滲透』。」該負責人說。該教堂信徒們認為這些措施實際上就是為了監控他們的一舉一動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/crosses-taken-off-26-three-self-churches-in-a-jiangxi-county/?source=zy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fcrosses-taken-off-26-three-self-churches-in-a-jiangxi-county%2F%3Fsource%3Dzy&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19mAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=1a89e640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/crosses-taken-off-26-three-self-churches-in-a-jiangxi-county/?source=zy</a>"},{"pid":"b8e14a7d138a4c59b5b10bfa1d13a10e356e0bb3","tid":2056160,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/190452_27c172cea0f0de329a8098d5376d34e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F190452_27c172cea0f0de329a8098d5376d34e1.png&h=9226a2fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e05613bed40ee34563a5b80ab3a01e2c6e589d","tid":2056160,"uid":167928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F32F26a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF32F26a.jpg&h=bdf5b931&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJYFiEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJYFiEv.jpg&h=b980ca1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5VkiEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5VkiEW.jpg&h=d6861772&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}